    },
    "body": "This PR fixes a TypeError that occurs when attempting to load models like Qwen3-30B-A3B.\n\nThe bug was introduced in commit [d979dd6bebb1857052e6beae682e5186f8447fde](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/commit/d979dd6bebb1857052e6beae682e5186f8447fde). In that commit, the return_success=True argument was added to the function call for moe_wna16_weight_loader, but the function's definition was not updated to accept this new argument.\n\nAs a result, the weight loading process failed with a TypeError when attempting to load models such as Qwen3 30B A3B.\n\nThis fix updates the function signature of moe_wna16_weight_loader to include the return_success parameter, allowing model loading to complete successfully.\n\nEDIT 250818:\n\nNow also fix this bug:\n\nAttributeError: 'MoeWNA16Method' object has no attribute 'moe'",
    "created_at": "2025-08-13T07:38:50Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-03-15T16:56:53Z",
